catmonthly: 
        Concatenate a bunch of monthly files together.
        Also, add two fields to each of the input files, and the final
        output file:
                - month (1-12)
                - ndays (# of days per month)

        - To use it, first modify the variables at the top of the
          script, then run it from the directory containing the monthly
          output files   

	- Can be used in conjunction with weighted_avg 
